sentences: Kim Jae-kyung (born December 24, 1988) is a South Korean actress and singer.
Kim was born in Seodaemun-gu, Seoul, South Korea on December 24, 1988.
On March 31, 2012, her major leading role, she portrayed Na Yoo-mi in the JTBC's drama Monster.
In 2016, she became a host on Beauty Bible, alongside Jessica Jung.
In December 2016, Kim signed with new management agency Namoo Actors to start afresh as an actress.
